32:35.954 --> 32:38.304
Ready to take on anyone.

32:38.347 --> 32:41.307
[crowds cheering]

32:41.350 --> 32:43.918
- Okay.
Once more with gusto.

32:43.962 --> 32:46.660
- Yeah, you might just
wanna lean into it.

32:48.270 --> 32:49.837
[bell dinging]

32:54.363 --> 32:58.367
- I've got a grand
that says my vamp here

32:58.411 --> 33:00.761
