33:21.651 --> 33:23.392
[crowd murmuring]

33:23.436 --> 33:25.090
- You got that vamp on lock!

33:25.133 --> 33:26.395
- You're on.

33:26.439 --> 33:29.398
[suspenseful music]

33:29.442 --> 33:31.792
- All right, let's do this!

33:31.835 --> 33:36.971
♪

33:37.015 --> 33:38.364
- Yeah!

33:38.407 --> 33:40.366
♪

33:40.409 --> 33:42.890
Yeah! Come on!

33:42.933 --> 33:44.500
- Whoo-hoo!

33:44.544 --> 33:46.720
- I think we need
to up the stakes.

33:46.763 --> 33:49.462
A vampire versus
an unturned were,

33:49.505 --> 33:52.726
that's not a fair fight!

33:52.769 --> 33:57.905
Now that's more like it!
The reigning champ returns.

33:57.948 --> 34:00.168
- [snarling]

34:00.212 --> 34:07.175
♪

34:07.219 --> 34:11.092
[crowd cheering]

34:11.136 --> 34:14.139
[dramatic music]

34:14.182 --> 34:19.492
♪

34:19.535 --> 34:21.015
- I know where Mary is.

34:21.059 --> 34:27.065
♪

34:27.108 --> 34:29.763
- [grunts]

34:29.806 --> 34:31.112
[kick lands]

34:31.156 --> 34:37.031
♪

34:37.075 --> 34:38.511
- Mary!

34:38.554 --> 34:40.687
- Olivia.

34:40.730 --> 34:42.819
- We're getting
you out of here.

34:46.084 --> 34:47.737
[clanging]

34:47.781 --> 34:50.697
♪

34:50.740 --> 34:52.133
Are you okay?

34:52.177 --> 34:54.353
- I'm sorry I left with her.
- It's not your fault.

34:54.396 --> 34:55.876
- We have got to go.

34:55.919 --> 34:57.704
♪

34:57.747 --> 35:00.881
- Wait.
I can't leave without my dad.

35:00.924 --> 35:05.886
♪

35:05.929 --> 35:08.149
[crowd cheering]

35:08.193 --> 35:11.196
[grunting]
[blows landing]

35:11.239 --> 35:14.199
[intense music]

35:14.242 --> 35:21.206
♪

35:21.249 --> 35:24.209
[crowd cheering]

35:24.252 --> 35:27.734
♪

35:27.777 --> 35:30.171
- Come on!
I got real money on the line!

35:30.215 --> 35:33.914
[snarling]

35:33.957 --> 35:41.008
♪

35:45.012 --> 35:46.187
- Lem!

35:46.231 --> 35:47.232
- Lem?

35:47.275 --> 35:49.234
- Lem!
Hammer time.

35:49.277 --> 35:51.410
- [shouting]

35:51.453 --> 35:54.413
[crowd cheering]

35:54.456 --> 35:56.980
[grunting]

36:01.071 --> 36:02.725
[bell clanging]

36:02.769 --> 36:08.253
[chanting]
Vamp, Vamp, Vamp, Vamp!

36:08.296 --> 36:09.341
- We don't have much time.

36:09.384 --> 36:10.603
- Let's get out of here.

36:10.646 --> 36:13.606
[suspenseful music]

36:13.649 --> 36:16.696
- Dude, we gotta let them out.

36:16.739 --> 36:18.611
They're victims.
We all are.

36:18.654 --> 36:19.786
- Please.

36:21.309 --> 36:22.441
[electric shocks]
[both shouting]

36:22.484 --> 36:23.833
- Get the hell out of here!

36:23.877 --> 36:27.315
Or I'll push this button
until they all fry!

36:27.359 --> 36:30.275
- Okay!
Okay.

36:30.318 --> 36:33.974
- [screaming]

36:34.017 --> 36:36.150
- [screams]

36:36.194 --> 36:37.934
Get that bitch!

36:37.978 --> 36:39.197
Get her!

36:39.240 --> 36:41.111
♪

36:41.155 --> 36:43.070
[all shouting]

36:43.113 --> 36:44.463
[metal clinking]

36:44.506 --> 36:48.336
[groaning]

36:48.380 --> 36:51.948
[screaming]

36:57.215 --> 36:57.389
.

36:57.432 --> 36:58.607
- Thank you so much.

36:58.651 --> 37:01.436
- Mmm.

37:01.480 --> 37:02.959
You're safe now.

37:03.003 --> 37:06.267
[dramatic music]

37:06.311 --> 37:08.487
- Dad, we have to go
back to Midnight.

37:08.530 --> 37:09.879
We'll be safe there.

37:09.923 --> 37:13.535
- Yeah, actually, sweetheart,
I was kinda hoping

37:13.579 --> 37:15.058
you'd come with me.

37:15.102 --> 37:16.930
There's a were safe haven
in Nevada.

37:16.973 --> 37:19.672
They'll protect us.

37:19.715 --> 37:21.239
- Can you come with us?

37:23.545 --> 37:25.286
- Midnight's our home.

37:25.330 --> 37:30.073
- But, uh, you and your dad
are welcome there anytime.

37:30.117 --> 37:32.293
- Yeah.

37:32.337 --> 37:35.122
But right now you need
to be with your dad.

37:38.125 --> 37:42.738
If I had a second
chance with my father,

37:42.782 --> 37:45.001
I wouldn't think twice.

37:47.656 --> 37:49.876
Remember what I told you?

37:49.919 --> 37:51.617
Girls like me and you...

37:51.660 --> 37:53.445
[exhales sharply]

37:53.488 --> 37:55.011
We're strong.

37:55.055 --> 37:57.144
- And special.

37:57.187 --> 37:59.407
[chuckles]
- Yeah.

37:59.451 --> 38:05.718
♪

38:05.761 --> 38:07.459
- [chuckles]

38:07.502 --> 38:11.114
♪

38:11.158 --> 38:14.335
