38:52.199 --> 38:54.941
- I ca--I can't.
- Uh...

38:54.984 --> 38:56.246
- Um...
- Of course.

38:56.290 --> 38:58.336
Um...
- Uh, it's been a long day.

38:58.379 --> 39:00.163
I'ma get some sleep.
I'll s--I'll see you around.

39:00.207 --> 39:02.340
- Okay, goodnight.

39:02.383 --> 39:04.733
- ♪ I put a spell on you

39:04.777 --> 39:06.996
- Unacceptable.

39:07.040 --> 39:08.607
[hisses]

39:08.650 --> 39:10.478
- It's only temporary.

39:10.522 --> 39:11.784
[sighs]

39:11.827 --> 39:14.961
I am so sorry, Bobo.

39:15.004 --> 39:16.658
I really didn't have a choice.

39:16.702 --> 39:18.704
It's the only way
to protect you.

39:18.747 --> 39:20.575
- [hisses]

39:20.619 --> 39:23.839
- But I promise it's only until
I figure out what to do

39:23.883 --> 39:25.014
about this curse.

39:25.058 --> 39:28.235
Oh.

39:28.278 --> 39:30.498
Please don't hate me.

39:30.542 --> 39:32.457
♪

39:32.500 --> 39:33.806
- Mmm.

39:33.849 --> 39:38.767
- ♪ I love you anyhow

39:38.811 --> 39:40.552
- [sighs]

39:43.772 --> 39:45.426
Did you mean what you said?

39:45.470 --> 39:47.123
About giving your dad
a second chance?

39:47.167 --> 39:48.603
- No, not in a million years.

39:48.647 --> 39:50.388
[sighs]

39:52.520 --> 39:57.395
- ♪ Because you're mine

39:57.438 --> 39:59.745
- It's okay to cry.

39:59.788 --> 40:02.661
- [scoffs]

40:02.704 --> 40:04.837
I'm fine.

40:07.970 --> 40:09.798
- I miss her, too.

40:14.977 --> 40:17.110
- It's so stupid.

40:18.459 --> 40:24.683
For--what--two days?
[scoffs]

40:28.469 --> 40:33.692
I don't know but it's
like we had a family.

40:33.735 --> 40:35.563
- ♪ I love you

40:35.607 --> 40:38.087
♪ I love you anyhow

40:38.131 --> 40:40.655
- [sighs]

